Class CKMS

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.safenetinc.jcprov.constants.CKMS

  • public class CKMS
extends java.lang.Object
    Class defining ProtectToolkit C CKMS_ constants - Elliptic Curve Encryption, MAC Scheme to be used.

    Further information concerning the various values is provided in the Programmers Manual.
